Description: TSO500R(eader) provides tools for importing, processing, and 
    analyzing data from Illumina TruSight Oncology 500 (TSO500) assays. 
    Supports data from the TSO500 DRAGEN analysis pipeline, DRAGEN ctDNA 
    analysis pipeline, and LocalApp. Functions include parsing quality control 
    files ('MetricsOutput.tsv'), processing variant analysis outputs 
    ('CombinedVariantOutput.tsv'), integrating different result types, 
    generating visualizations, and exporting data for downstream analysis.
